{
  "text": "In [CITATION_1] Zhang performs a visual comparison to aerial photos by overlaying the obtained footprints over the aerial image to determine how accurate the LIDAR building footprints were. Contrary to Zhang, this particular satellite comparison algorithm attempts to provide a tool to compare the obtained LIDAR footprints to satellite imagery automatically.",
